cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Triple-Penalty Mobility-Justice Diagnostic on 34,858 French Communes"
message: >-
  If you use this analysis, please cite both the paper (note + URL
  below) and this repository.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Fossé
    given-names: Rohan
    email: rfosse@cesi.fr
    affiliation: CESI École d'Ingénieurs, Montpellier, France
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0002-2195-0198"
  - family-names: Pallares
    given-names: Gaël
    affiliation: CESI LINEACT (EA 7527), Montpellier, France
