repository-code: "https://github.com/cycling-data-lab/penality-analysis"
url: "https://github.com/cycling-data-lab/penality-analysis"
abstract: >-
  Code and reproducible LaTeX for the paper "Cycling poverty in
  France: a triple-penalty mobility-justice diagnostic on 34,858
  communes". The triple-penalty index overlays cycling-environment
  deprivation, monetary-poverty exposure and structural geographic
  isolation on the IMD-4 substrate and identifies 322 priority
  communes, including a 90-commune metropolitan-extreme subset
  invisible under any standard single-axis equity filter.
keywords:
  - cycling poverty
  - mobility justice
  - transport equity
  - composite indicator
  - commune-level diagnostic
  - Plan Vélo
  - overseas territories
